name: Proof Gift Card - $50
description:
Do you want to get some Proof Wood Eyewear for someone, but you just can't decide what they'll like? get them the Proof Gift Card and let them decide.

This is how it works:
-Proof Gift Cards can be ordered on our on-line store
-Within 3 days you will receive an e-mail with the gift card attached
-It can be either printed out or forwarded to the recipient
-The attachment will include a unique code that can be used on the on-line store only.
-Proof gift card codes can only be used on time
-Proof gift card never expires
